      "type": "text",
      "required": true,
      "default": "Enersok FE LLC was formed in 2022 by the Consortium of Electricite De France (EDF), Nebras Power (Qatar), Sojitz Corporation and Kyuden International (Japan), which entered into public-private partnership agreement for construction of a Gas Combined Cycle Power Plant with capacity of 1,6 GW in Syrdarya region, Uzbekistan (On March 25, 2022). "
